cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.PL

The paper deals with secure search over encrypted data, which falls under the category of cryptography (cs.CR). It also presents a hardware-based approach for implementing a highly performant encrypted database index, which involves database systems (cs.DB) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The use of Intel's SGX also suggests a focus on software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL).
